{"tid":2496290,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［回帶］海天堂龜苓膏 喺2013年 被揭發以水喉水清洗發霉龜苓膏賣俾客 及啲膏只含極微量龜成份","createTime":"2021-04-19T17:04:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T04:26:45.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"be5652d340293e81e0f3665254fa310dd2eb0a39","tid":2496290,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T17:04:25.000Z","msg":"龜苓膏名牌海天堂繼被揭發以水喉水清洗發霉龜苓膏售賣給顧客後，再被驗出所售的龜苓膏「冇龜」。城市大學生物及化學系抽驗市面4個品牌的龜苓膏，發現海天堂其中一個保鮮裝龜苓膏樣本完全沒有龜板成份，其餘兩個樣本只含極微量，<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">學者形容「同食涼粉冇分別」，並無滋陰功效</span></span></strong>，也涉違反《商品說明條例》。<br />\n<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20130912/MABQIQNZKBNCO34DNG7MQ5AHWE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20130912%2FMABQIQNZKBNCO34DNG7MQ5AHWE&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuH4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=1e109e88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20130912%2FMABQIQNZKBNCO34DNG7MQ5AHWE&h=1e004ac7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20130912/MABQIQNZKBNCO34DNG7MQ5AHWE</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n龜苓膏連鎖店海天堂2013年遭《蘋果日報》踢爆疑將發霉龜苓膏清洗出售，引發退款潮。海天堂隨即控告向《蘋果》爆料的公司前股東蔡國強誹謗，指他設局拍攝洗霉片段，惡意損害海天堂，案件昨在高院開審。<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">海天堂老闆「鬍鬚佬」坦言龜苓膏發霉是普遍問題，又承認當年送貨貨車無冷凍設備</span></span></strong>，但他強調「冷氣開好大。」<br />\n<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201007/LHEHAZHSXZBVNAGGFDMRBEYFLI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201007%2FLHEHAZHSXZBVNAGGFDMRBEYFLI%2F&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuH4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=7f935f12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201007%2FLHEHAZHSXZBVNAGGFDMRBEYFLI%2F&h=12c0adcb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201007/LHEHAZHSXZBVNAGGFDMRBEYFLI/</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n依家海天堂仲要做埋藍店<br />\n喺cctvb落廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">🚫 海天堂 🚫</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hoitintonghk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhoitintonghk&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuH4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=ba44f474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hoitintonghk</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://pili.app/pg/16RCV8n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpili.app%2Fpg%2F16RCV8n&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuH4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=63464198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://pili.app/pg/16RCV8n</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUTZ687RFL2M5PYJ7438s6JL2GyUwafWidevuYJdWGwXV?filename=P6mXPPs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP6mXPPs.jpg&h=48304d7d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f3daeadb85a690e58703c0e40da2be73623377d","tid":2496290,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T17:04:42.000Z","msg":"原post<br />\n<br />\n[無龜嘅龜苓膏]海天堂榮獲TVB最強人氣品牌大獎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2495939\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2495939</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d1f2913efd106bd9edac45bc299f9328216ba11e","tid":2496290,"uid":350350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T01:19:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ec83e5c7f77a32c45cbab8c93690a7bee86369c","tid":2496290,"uid":364850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T01:50:42.000Z","msg":"仲未執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f22c48576f7c952eb97f1051c86f0781b3888c0","tid":2496290,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ec83e5c7f77a32c45cbab8c93690a7bee86369c","tid":2496290,"uid":364850,"like":0,"dis